## Data License

The datasets generated by this software may be subject to different licenses
depending on the data sources:

- SIATA data: Check https://siata.gov.co for terms of use
- OpenAQ data: CC BY 4.0 (https://openaq.org/about/license)
- ERA5 data: Copernicus License (https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu/api/v2/terms/static/licence-to-use-copernicus-products.pdf)
- CAMS data: Copernicus License (same as above)

Please cite the original data sources when using the combined dataset.
